com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Class ReadCustomerReturnsService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.ReadCustomerReturnsService

  • public class ReadCustomerReturnsService
extends Object

    This service enables external applications to integrate with read methods for processing customer returns in SAP S/4HANA Cloud. It enables you to retrieve customer returns in an API call.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_CUSTOMER_RETURN_SRV
    API Version:1
    Minimum ERP Version:1708
    Communication Scenario:Customer Return Integration (SAP_COM_0157)
    Scope Items:Accelerated Customer Returns (BKP)
